            <title><![CDATA[中联部部长刘建超应约与美大使会面]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/articles/2023/04/20/002.jpg?VersionId=CieeHCvz7GtzrWN03e.GVDj_P6ol5tIR&amp;itok=DWFqq4_o" title="中共中央对外联络部星期四（4月20日）在官网发布照片，显示中联部部长刘建超（长桌右边中间）与美国驻华大使伯恩斯（左边中间）会面。（中联部官网）" alt="中共中央对外联络部星期四（4月20日）在官网发布照片，显示中联部部长刘建超（长桌右边中间）与美国驻华大使伯恩斯（左边中间）会面。（中联部官网）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/articles/2023/04/20/002.jpg?VersionId=CieeHCvz7GtzrWN03e.GVDj_P6ol5tIR&amp;itok=DWFqq4_o" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
